SQL_STMT_U.val: select count(*) from tosa_calc_header ch inner join producten_per_relatie pp on pp.ppr_id=ch.parent_ppr_id where ch.tax_year=~1 and ch.is_termination=~2 and ch.BASE_AMOUNT_OVER_THRESHOLD=1 and ch.DATE_CUSTOMER_LETTER_CREATED IS NOT NULL and (ch.DATE_CUSTOMER_LETTER_CREATED <= to_date(~3,'YYYYMMDD')) and (ch.IS_PROCESSED is null OR ch.IS_PROCESSED=0) and (~4=0 or pp.ppr_relatienummer >=~4) and (~5=999999999 or pp.ppr_relatienummer <=~5) and (~6=0 OR pp.PPR_PRODUCTNUMMER>=~6) and (~7=9999 OR pp.PPR_PRODUCTNUMMER<=~7) and (~4 <> ~5 OR ~6 <> ~7 OR pp.PPR_VOLGNR_PER_PRODUCT between ~8 AND ~9)
